==English==

===Etymology===
[[auto-]], self, and [[mobile]], as the vehicle is powered by an engine rather than pulled by horses.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{US}}: An enclosed [[passenger]] [[vehicle]] powered by an [[engine]].

